Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wonder Hill \N Let's Have Lots of Fun\NMaiden Mannerism\NReconciliation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maiden Mannerism\NReconciliation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, are all of you okay, \Ncoming here during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off-duty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free until university second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have the day off of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ishida, what sort of work do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you don't have to be so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all good people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not tense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The merry-go-round!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked with Tohya to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was you, Koide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mai and Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, great to see you!\NIt's good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Will things be all right?\NPlease have a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Magnolia"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Meg's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked it up on the viewing platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, then she's been by the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She could've actually said hello, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so like Meg to be nearby, \Nyet unable to come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To Megumi's home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... so, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know where it is, shall I go by there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go out to meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, New Leader! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So... if possible, please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring Miss Okura back, without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that Megumi wants to come back. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The young miss would be at school presently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,True, she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Around what time will she return home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I am afraid the young miss \Nhas been rather agitated of late...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say that, even if you waited for her, \Nyou likely would not be able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have... a card that Megumi dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't I at least hand this back to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon my rudeness, but might you be \Ntwo of the young miss's card-playing friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In my role as caretaker, \NI cannot allow you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In point of fact, I am also in charge of \Ntransporting her to and from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so you would not be able to meet her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider: the only time I do not watch over her \Nis while she is inside the school building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time that \Nshe has had friends such as yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, the young miss \Nappears to be having difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in matters where I am unable to be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Raika Academy High-School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If at all possible, could I trouble you \Nto visit her at her school?\NRaika Academy High-School Division
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dignified posture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mystical gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime... she truly is \Nthe pride of Raika Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Raika Academy, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a super-prestigious school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be okay, against their security?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about it, Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teito University has a bunch of \NRaika graduates, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note... are you okay, \Nnot being at school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, I thought of a way \Nwe could get into Raika Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're home late, Akiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Another hot guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu says he's a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for always looking after Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drop by suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he has business with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! And here I am, \Nhaving taken a break from love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what about me?! \NI'm currently accepting applications!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But didn't you graduate from there, Akiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could go in with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get inside, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Raika Academy has never \Nallowed in men from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That does sound like a rich girl's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How Akiko managed to get into a school \Nlike that is a mystery to me even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what business do you have at Raika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... want to go see a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you've got a friend who's a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, she's a friend, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bit of business with that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! You already have a girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was... a bit of a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it turned into something like a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make up with her, so Yu-yu and I \Nwere talking about visiting her at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu, you're wanting to \Nmediate in your friends' fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's basically it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu is truly kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely collaborate with you on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so will I!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...if men aren't allowed inside, \Nthere's no sense in visiting the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you held onto that uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The key point today is the makeup job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there isn't any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But this sort of natural look \Nis the hardest to manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So this was an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,However many times I see it, it's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're able to do makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After being forced to umpteen times, \Nyou start getting the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something you could normally--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No talking.\NThat's not something you could normally--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With good raw material, \Nyou've really outdone yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu! You really are incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-yu Kondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohko Ebata!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's time to head into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are we heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's keep walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall broach the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is "go" time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me! Will you not be leaving early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If at all possible, \Nwould you care to join us for tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She even looks lovely \Nwhen giving a curt rejection!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are... they acquaintances of yours, Meg Gloria? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... er, yes, acquaintances, I suppose \Nyou could say they are acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter, Meg Gloria?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is sweat upon \Nthe sculptural beauty of your brow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna report you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "Meg Gloria"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will report you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a state Miss Meg Gloria is in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be... suspicious individuals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is a transfer student \Nand an acquaintance of Miss Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And, um, this person here is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...my... mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! In that case, \Nyou ought to have said so sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then. I shall promptly \Nescort them to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Meg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are a transfer student and her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And being your acquaintances, \Nthey are all the more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we perhaps offer them a tour of the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a lovely idea. Shall I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, Madame Tohko and Miss Yu-yu, \Nyou even knew Meg Gloria as a small child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What was Meg Gloria like as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, let me see... she was very energetic, \Nand often prone to smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? I-Is that not the case now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Meg Gloria is very quiet and dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dignified?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu-yu, how did you become \Nacquaintanced with Meg Gloria?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um, I met Miss Megumi at Vanga--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Violin lessons!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness! Meg Gloria plays the violin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How sublime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but what is this "Meg Gloria" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gloria" is a hymn of glory from the Latin Mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria has told us of this herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that she is not accustomed to \Nshowing her emotions outwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Desiring to sing the praises of her cool beauty, \Nwe originally addressed her as Lady Meg,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but when we added "Gloria" \Nand addressed her as Meg Gloria instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she had one of her rare moments \Nof displaying great joy, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you two barge into \Nmy private affairs disguised as women?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Disguised as women?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you two come here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to see you, Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dreadful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Meg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been kidnapped by hooligans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.11,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna come in here, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria!\NMeg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg... Gloria...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,On the viewing platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... I know I'm in no position \Nto be requesting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you wreck Wonder Hill?  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I highly doubt that you'd understand this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to become strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...I discarded absolutely everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to win, and in order to win, I had to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only route I could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I activated that switch, \Nassuming that it would force a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one who goes to extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I chose one thing \Nand discarded everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still not sure whether or not \Nthat was truly for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But because I did so, \NI wound up truly hurting you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I understand that feeling, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had times where I wondered if \NI'd be better off just discarding everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I went to meet with Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:20:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For just one moment... \Nfor one single moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...I thought that I didn't need anything: \Nnot my home, not my school, not even Blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bro said to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"You shouldn't just throw it all away." 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't throw any of it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you threw it all away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For the rest of my life, \NI'll never be able to forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I understand a bit of \Nhow you feel, so that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And hang on, just how long \Ndo we need to stay crammed in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg Gloria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:20:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they hurt you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooligans! Let Meg Gloria go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooligans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're certainly not wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these people are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg... Gloria...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you're like at school, Okura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone unsmiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone super-cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I wanted myself to be a bit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with trying to look good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want me to stay with Blackout, \Nthen remember one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't pry too much \Ninto members' life situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackout welcomes all comers. That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She really did come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Meg!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yu-yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for keeping your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Camera test, camera test!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting video feed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello-break, Daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your leader: Mirei! 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a friendly match today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Word on the street says they're a famous team, \Nso my heart's going pitter-pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my very best, for the sake of \Nall of you cheering me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There were many others, besides me, \Nwho were asked to cooperate in the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make amends for upsetting all of you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go and stop them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because I want to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I'm with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...I won't let you do anything \Nweird like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.37,0:23:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.91,0:25:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.00,0:25:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Check Out My Card!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.68,0:25:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yu-yu!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.68,0:25:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll introduce Vairina Exspecta!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Exspecta is an additional overDress to put \Non a unit that already has an overDress!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:25:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Accordingly, its skill is super-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.07,0:26:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When attacking, it gets \N+15,000 power and an extra critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.88,0:26:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, once the battle ends, \Nyou discard all the originalDress units.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.94,0:26:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On your next turn, you can immediately \Nreuse Trickstar from the Drop Zone!\NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.53,0:26:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued \NA Piece of Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.87,0:26:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Episode 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nordlinger\NInfiltration 
